<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻|路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - 由 RSSHub 提供支持</description><lastBuildDate>Wed, 30 Oct 2024 03:21:19 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>亚洲股市因中国不利因素而下跌；黄金和比特币上涨</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-10-30/</link><description>由于中国疲软，亚洲股市周三下跌，投资者准备迎接竞争激烈的美国大选，尽管北京方面试图提振经济增长，但这场大选可能对世界第二大经济体产生巨大影响。</description><pubDate>Wed, 30 Oct 2024 02:45:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/global-markets-wrapup-1-2024-10-30/</guid></item><item><title>随着印太地区进入新导弹时代，澳大利亚将提高导弹产量</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/australia-ramp-up-missile-production-indo-pacific-enters-new-missile-age-2024-10-30/</link><description>澳大利亚表示，由于对中国在南太平洋试射洲际弹道导弹的“严重担忧”，澳大利亚正在增强其导弹防御能力，并将随着该地区进入新的“导弹时代”而加强武器库存和向安全伙伴的出口。</description><pubDate>Wed, 30 Oct 2024 01:58:45 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/australia-ramp-up-missile-production-indo-pacific-enters-new-missile-age-2024-10-30/</guid></item><item><title>安全官员称巴西军方将在G20峰会期间加强里约安全</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/americas/brazils-military-reinforce-rio-security-during-g20-summit-security-official-says-2024-10-29/</link><description>巴西安全国务秘书周二表示，下个月在里约热内卢举行的 20 国集团主要经济体会议期间，巴西将动用武装部队加强安全。</description><pubDate>Tue, 29 Oct 2024 23:06:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/americas/brazils-military-reinforce-rio-security-during-g20-summit-security-official-says-2024-10-29/</guid></item><item><title>美国大选对中国市场有何影响</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/whats-stake-chinas-markets-us-election-2024-10-29/</link><description>中国的货币和股市将首当其冲地受到美国保护主义转变的影响，并且人们认为其交易对选举的贸易和外交政策影响非常敏感。</description><pubDate>Tue, 29 Oct 2024 23:03:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china/whats-stake-chinas-markets-us-election-2024-10-29/</guid></item><item><title>早盘竞价：中国“火箭筒”失败，美元走强</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-2024-10-29/</link><description>展望未来一天的亚洲市场。</description><pubDate>Tue, 29 Oct 2024 21:48:35 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/global-markets-view-asia-graphic-2024-10-29/</guid></item><item><title>First Solar表示几家大型竞争对手正在侵犯专利</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/first-solar-says-several-large-rivals-are-infringing-patents-2024-10-29/</link><description>美国太阳能电池板制造商 First Solar 高管在周二与分析师举行的电话会议上表示，该公司已通知几家大型竞争对手，认为它们侵犯了其领先太阳能技术的专利。</description><pubDate>Tue, 29 Oct 2024 21:39:09 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/energy/first-solar-says-several-large-rivals-are-infringing-patents-2024-10-29/</guid></item><item><title>戴姆勒卡车评估中国业务，估值达1.95亿美元</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/daimler-truck-assesses-china-business-flags-195-mln-valuation-hit-2024-10-29/</link><description>德国戴姆勒卡车公司周二表示，由于中国卡车市场复苏仍难以实现，该公司正在评估其中国业务的未来，并表示将收取 1.8 亿欧元（1.95 亿美元）的一次性估值调整费用。</description><pubDate>Tue, 29 Oct 2024 20:57:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/daimler-truck-assesses-china-business-flags-195-mln-valuation-hit-2024-10-29/</guid></item><item><title>据《纽约时报》报道，特朗普家族、拜登助手是中国黑客攻击目标</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/cybersecurity/trump-family-biden-aides-among-china-hack-targets-nyt-reports-2024-10-29/</link><description>《纽约时报》周二援引知情人士的话报道称，美国前总统唐纳德·特朗普的家人和拜登政府的官员都是与中国有关的黑客的攻击目标，这些黑客能够侵入电信公司的系统。</description><pubDate>Tue, 29 Oct 2024 19:55:42 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/cybersecurity/trump-family-biden-aides-among-china-hack-targets-nyt-reports-2024-10-29/</guid></item><item><title>特别报道：英特尔内部，首席执行官帕特·基辛格（Pat Gelsinger）摸索着美国偶像的复兴</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/inside-intel-ceo-pat-gelsinger-fumbled-revival-an-american-icon-2024-10-29/</link><description>英特尔与台湾台积电达成了一项甜蜜的协议，台积电将生产英特尔设计但无法生产的芯片。消息人士称，它还向英特尔提供大幅折扣。</description><pubDate>Tue, 29 Oct 2024 17:35:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/inside-intel-ceo-pat-gelsinger-fumbled-revival-an-american-icon-2024-10-29/</guid></item><item><title>ASMI 上调人工智能指引，中国需求依然强劲</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/asmis-third-quarter-bookings-beat-expectations-ups-guidance-2024-10-29/</link><description>芯片制造设备供应商 ASM 国际 (ASMI) 周二预测，由于人工智能继续推动高端订单，而中国订单降幅小于预期，第三季度预订量超出预期，因此第四季度指引将上调。</description><pubDate>Tue, 29 Oct 2024 17:23:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/asmis-third-quarter-bookings-beat-expectations-ups-guidance-2024-10-29/</guid></item><item><title>全球需求疲软，Moncler 第三季度销售额下滑 3%</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/sales-moncler-slip-3-third-quarter-global-demand-weakens-2024-10-29/</link><description>按固定汇率计算，意大利奢侈外套制造商 Moncler 第三季度收入下降 3%，略高于分析师预期，其所有主要市场均表现疲软。</description><pubDate>Tue, 29 Oct 2024 16:50:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/sales-moncler-slip-3-third-quarter-global-demand-weakens-2024-10-29/</guid></item><item><title>欧盟对中国电动汽车征收关税，可能会遭到北京方面的强烈反对</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/eu-slaps-tariffs-chinese-evs-risking-beijing-payback-2024-10-29/</link><description>在最引人注目的贸易调查结束后，欧盟决定将中国制造的电动汽车的关税提高至高达 45.3%，该调查导致欧洲分裂并引发北京方面的报复。</description><pubDate>Tue, 29 Oct 2024 16:46:41 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/eu-slaps-tariffs-chinese-evs-risking-beijing-payback-2024-10-29/</guid></item><item><title>法国部长就“政治”干邑关税挑战中国</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/french-minister-challenge-china-over-political-cognac-duties-2024-10-29/</link><description>两位法国外交消息人士周二表示，当法国贸易部长索菲·普里马斯下周访问上海时，法国将就白兰地进口关税问题向中国发起挑战，巴黎方面称此举具有政治性且不合理。</description><pubDate>Tue, 29 Oct 2024 14:57:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/french-minister-challenge-china-over-political-cognac-duties-2024-10-29/</guid></item><item><title>芬兰警告习近平朝鲜在乌克兰战争中“挑衅”</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/finlands-president-raises-ukraine-war-security-issues-with-chinas-xi-2024-10-29/</link><description>芬兰总统亚历山大·斯塔布表示，他周二在北京会谈期间代表北约和欧盟向中国国家主席习近平表示，朝鲜与俄罗斯的活动是升级和挑衅。</description><pubDate>Tue, 29 Oct 2024 11:53:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/finlands-president-raises-ukraine-war-security-issues-with-chinas-xi-2024-10-29/</guid></item><item><title>小米推出更快版旗舰电动车挑战特斯拉</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/xiaomi-chief-touts-nurburgring-record-ahead-ev-launch-2024-10-29/</link><description>小米周二推出了 SU7 电动跑车的豪华版，称这款售价 114,000 美元的车型将成为量产中最快的四门汽车，直接挑战特斯拉和保时捷等公司。</description><pubDate>Tue, 29 Oct 2024 10:16:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/xiaomi-chief-touts-nurburgring-record-ahead-ev-launch-2024-10-29/</guid></item></channel></rss>